parameters: Well well, what do we have here?
Um... I've been cursed by a demonic dog...
A curse? Does that make your belly grow bigger?
Please explain the situation in detail.

I was forcefully... made to have sex... and he
came inside me.
Did you have sex with a demonic dog?!

And... because of the curse, my body became
capable of getting pregnant immediately...

The school nurse said that if I go to the chapel,
everything will be okay.

Yes, it is indeed possible to remove the child
from your womb.

There have been students who become pregnant while
attending school.

For that reason, the Sisters at Samuel Chapel are
assigned Sisters who are knowledgeable in medical
care.

Even when you have a serious injury, I will be the
one to administer first aid.

However, what is inside your belly is a child of a
monster, isn't it?

By studying magic and being in close proximity to
demons and monsters, that's how it happens.
As expected, humans should not use magic, right?

Now is not the time to be saying such things,
right?

And... Amelia is a victim who was forced against
her will.

We cannot simply take in a child of monsters
within the church grounds.

If you do that, even the naughty children who use
magic should be forgiven.

(I want to punch her, but I can only rely on
Sister...)

(They're saying it knowing that I can't refuse
either)
Then, please step forward, the person next to you.

I'm sure she would feel embarrassed being seen as
a man too.
I'm fine, so please go back already.

I don't want the person I like to see me in such a
pathetic state...

For now, should we go to the student council room?
I think it was on the 4th floor.

The lewdness level increased by 5! The pregnancy
count increased by 1! The climax count increased
by 3! The squirting count increased by 1!
